track.name: Trouble Weighs A Ton
comments: new sons of anarchy teaser huh

Well....this has come up on my radio and I feel I have to comment. I have bought a few of Dan Auerbach's discs in the last few weeks. All are brilliant but this song is fast becoming a real favourite..........it is brilliant...........
Yes.....well on its way to becoming a real favourite of mine.......Trouble...........killing me........dear mother.......trouble weighs a ton....

Trouble killin' me 
Whoa, it's killin' me
"Needles and things... like the setting sun" - Neil Young reference? The Needle and the Damage Done last line...
A great start to a unbelievable album...outstanding talent.
Oh, dear God. This is beautiful.
what a perfect start for the album.
